<% layout("../layouts/boilerplate.ejs") %>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/pages/faqs.css">

<div class="faq-page">
    <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="page-header">
            <i class="bi bi-question-circle"></i>
            <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
            <p>Find quick answers to the most commonly asked questions about VibeStay.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-card">

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3><i class="bi bi-search"></i> How do I find a property?</h3>
                <p>Use the search and filter options on the listings page to find accommodations based on location, property type, price, and amenities.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3><i class="bi bi-calendar-check"></i> How do I make a booking?</h3>
                <p>Open a listing, select your dates, choose available rooms, and submit a booking request. The host must approve the request before it becomes confirmed.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3><i class="bi bi-x-circle"></i> Can I cancel my booking?</h3>
                <p>Yes. Approved bookings can be cancelled up to 24 hours before the check-in date, subject to platform policies.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3><i class="bi bi-house-door"></i> How do I become a host?</h3>
                <p>Create an account, add your property details, upload images, configure rooms and pricing, and publish your listing.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3><i class="bi bi-heart"></i> How does the wishlist work?</h3>
                <p>Click the wishlist icon on any property to save it for future viewing. You can access saved properties from your dashboard.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3><i class="bi bi-shield-lock"></i> Is my personal information secure?</h3>
                <p>Yes. VibeStay uses secure authentication and follows industry-standard practices to protect user information.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3><i class="bi bi-key"></i> I forgot my password. What should I do?</h3>
                <p>Use the "Forgot Password" option on the login page and follow the OTP verification process to reset your password.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3><i class="bi bi-chat-dots"></i> How can I contact support?</h3>
                <p>Visit the Contact Us page to reach our support team through email or other available support channels.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
